<HEADLINE> Beijing Switch Producer Gets ISO-9001 Certification </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 5 (Xinhua) -- The Beijing Switch Plant was
given its ISO-9001 certification by the SGS Yarsley Company today.
</P>
<P>
The plant is the first Chinese switch manufacturer whose
products have met internationally-required quality standards.
</P>
<P>
This state-owned company mainly produces electrical appliances,
power distribution products, and control systems for nuclear power
plants, and spends 3.5 percent of its annual profits on technical
renovation to improve product quality.  
</P>
