provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities participating in
the exhibition, which covers 14,400 sq.m. An outdoor section
covers 4,000 sq.m.
</P>
<P>
Seventeen areas pay tribute the the country's economic reform,
the opening up, national strength, macro-economic controls,
cultural progress, and the blueprint for the next century.
</P>
<P>
The Regional Hall has 31 exhibition areas depicting
achievements of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities.
</P>
<P>
The event is being organized by the Propaganda Department of
the CPC Central Committee, the State Planning Commission, the
State Economic and Trade Commission, the State Commission for
Restructuring the Economy, and the State Statistics Bureau.
</P>
<P>
