<HEADLINE> 5 Dead, 400 Hospitalized in Food Poisoning in India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, September 6 (Xinhua) -- Five people, including four
children, died and at least 400 were hospitalized in India's
Kerala State after suffering from food poisoning on Friday
evening, Press Trust of India said today.
</P>
<P>
