mussels, a variety of shell fish, during the day on Friday and
developed vomiting and discomfort by the evening.
</P>
<P>
A 33-year-old woman and four children under the age of 10 died
on Friday night. More than 400 people were hospitalized in three
local government hospitals.
</P>
<P>
The condition of 10 admitted to the government hospitals was
stated to be serious, police said, adding that it was not
immediately known if anybody was admitted in private hospitals.
