<HEADLINE> Mansoura Beats Jomo Cosmos 3-0 in African Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, September 6 (Xinhua) -- Mansoura of Egypt hammered Jomo
Cosmos of South Africa 3-0 in the African Cup Winners' Cup
quarter-final first leg matches played in Mansoura on Friday.
</P>
<P>
The home team led 1-0 in the first half. Emad Salama opened the
socrings for Mansoura nine minutes go to the match.
</P>
