were immediately broken back by Kafelnikov and Vacek.
</P>
<P>
Bjorkman is still in contention for the singles championship
and will play Briton Greg Rusedski on Saturday in the semifinals.
</P>
<P>
Kafelnikov and Vacek earned 150,000 U.S. dollars each while
Bjorkman and Kulti sharing another 150,000 dollars. 
