who will be reorientated by leaving their present assignments for
others where their professional skills will be of maximum use.
</P>
<P>
The minister has challenged the private sector to fill the
vacume created by the disengagement of the state from the
productive circles of the cameroonian economy.
</P>
<P>
He stressed the need for sensitisation and training of workers
to improve their efficiency.
</P>
<P>
The seminar opened yesterday and is closing here this evening.
